name: exit
description: Terminate the current EScheme session with <integer-exit-code> (defaults to 0).

name: load
description: Reads and evaluates <filename-str>'s EScheme contents in the global environment.

name: system
description:
Executes a command, using the environment variable bindings in
<env-var-str-list> (defaults to the current environment), in
the <directory-str> directory (defaults to the current working directory).
Passed to Java's <Runtime.getRuntime().exec()>.
Returns a list:
  (<command-stdout-str> <command-stderr-str> <command-exit-code>)
